{
  "texts": [
    "Large AI model trainingThe enormous number of parameters has significantly increased the training time of large AI models, leading to a significant increase in computational costs [167].",
    "According to a report published by Guosheng Securities [168], the cost of training GPT-3 is estimated to be approximately $1.4 million per session.",
    "For larger LLM models, the training cost ranges from $2 million to $12 million, including GPU costs, data center costs, labor costs, and other hardware costs.It is now necessary to reconsider the training architecture of large AI models, the choice of parallel strategies, and efficient data storage and communication methods.",
    "Currently, several training frameworks have emerged in the field of large AI models.",
    "Some of the more wellknown ones include Microsoft's DeepSpeed and NVIDIA's Megatron-LM [169]."
  ]
}